<snippet>
	<content><![CDATA[const RGBToHex = (r, g, b) => ((r << 16) + (g << 8) + b).toString(16).padStart(6, '0');]]></content>
	<description>Converts the values of RGB components to a color code.  Convert given RGB parameters to hexadecimal string using bitwise left-shift operator (`<<`) and `toString(16)`, then `padStart(6,'0')` to get a 6-digit hexadecimal value.</description>
